name: Mind Architect
description:
I am a person who often gets lost in my own head. I've never had a comfortable space in there. Because in the end I just made room after room new in my mind. The rooms mixed and melted into each other and became strange lumps. Sometimes I can't recognize myself when I see what's inside my head.

"How come something like that exists in my head?", exactly like that every time I was thinking.

- SK00L
